# Tauri Narratrix APP
## Tech Stack:
- Backend: Rust
- Database: SQLite
- Frontend: React (Deno) and Vite

## Folder Structure
narratrix/
├── src-tauri/          # Rust backend code
├── src/                # React frontend code
├── public/             # Static assets
├── tests/              # Test files
├── deno.json          # Deno configuration
├── import_map.json    # Deno import map
└── tauri.conf.json    # Tauri configuration

## Workflow setup
- Be mindful if dependencies are for development and use the appropriate flags

## Coding Standards
- Use TypeScript for all new code
- Use proper TypeScript types for all variables, functions and return types
- Implement proper error handling and input validation
- Always use relative imports

## Best Practices
- Ensure secure, efficient code following Tauri and Rust best practices
- Focus on performance and readability